Activating Bonus Bet: Second Chance Scatter™: 1. Doubles the bet; 2. Randomly activates the Second Chance Scatter™ Re-Spin if 2 Scatter or Wild symbols landed on the reels. The reels that do not have a Wild or a Scatter symbol on them re-spin for a chance to get another Scatter symbol on the reels and activate Free Spins.
The Bonus Bet: Second Chance Scatter™ can be activated and deactivated in the main game.

Symbols appear in stacks in both the main game (randomly) and Free Spins (always).
The reels the Wild or Scatter symbols landed on to activate Free Spins, become hot.
Serpent Stacks landing on hot reels expand to cover the entire reel.
There are 4 types of Wild symbols: a single Serpent Wild, 2 expanding Serpent Wilds, and Serpent Stacks.
The single Serpent Wild appears on the first or the third row only.
The expanding Serpent Wild symbols expand either up or down, and may or may not cover the entire reel.
The Serpent Stacks appear only in Free Spins on hot reels and will cover the entire reel.
All the Wild symbols, except for the single Serpent Wild, substitute for all symbols.
